# Category

## Create category
Endpoint: api/v3/category/create
Method: POST
Example request: 
{
    "data": {
        "name": "Scaled metal models",
        "image": "https://static.dev.alephexpress.com/api/file/get/e4586ac1-09cb-48cf-ab45-7341f04995d3/16ced3c00a1e550b79f7f7519a1f075e_1702474108.JPG",
        "showOnMain": true
    }
}


Field name
Type
Requirements
Limitations
name
string
Required
Min - 1; max - 255
image
string (url)
Optional 
Min - 1; max - 255
showOnMain
boolean
Required
true, false


Example response:
{
    "data": {
        "id": 25,
        "name": "Scaled metal models 2",
        "slug": "scaled-metal-models-2",
        "showOnMain": true,
        "sortIndex": 24,
        "itemsCount": 0,
        "image": "https://static.dev.alephexpress.com/api/file/get/e4586ac1-09cb-48cf-ab45-7341f04995d3/16ced3c00a1e550b79f7f7519a1f075e_1702474108.JPG",
        "metaTitle": null,
        "metaDescription": null
    }
}

Field name
Type
Requirements
Limitations
Description
id
integer
Required
Bigint
System identifier (auto increment)
name
string
Required
Min - 1; max - 255
Value provided in request
slug
string
Optional
Min - 1; max - 255
Descriptive unique text that identifies the category
showOnMain
boolean
Required
true, false
Value provided in request;category displays on main page if true
sortIndex
integer
Required
Bigint
Defines the item display order
itemsCount
integer
Required
Positive integer
Quantity of products in the category
image
string (url)
Optional 
Min - 1; max - 255
Value provided in request
metaTitle
string
Optional 
Min - 1; max - 60
Available if SEO plugin is activated
metaDescription
string
Optional 
Min - 1; max - 160
Available if SEO plugin is activated

Update category
Endpoint: api/v3/category/update
Method: POST
Example request: 
{
    "data": {
        "id": "1",
        "name": "Clothes",
        "image": "img.jpg",
        "showOnMain": true
    }
}


Field name
Type
Requirements
Limitations
id
integer
Required
Exists in the system
