Update Categories Order
Endpoint: api/v3/category/update-order
Method: POST
Example request: 
{
    "data": {
        "items": [
{
‚Äúid‚Äù: 1,
‚ÄúsortIndex‚Äù : 2
},
{
‚Äúid‚Äù: 2,
‚ÄúsortIndex‚Äù: 1
}
]
    }
}

Field name
Type
Requirements
Limitations
items
Array of objects
Required
Number of items is limited only by PHP logic
id
integer
Required
Exists in the system
sortIndex
integer
Required
Defines the item display order


Example response:
{}
Empty object returns in case of successful categories order change
Delete Categories
Endpoint: api/v3/category/delete
Method: POST
Example request: 
{
    "data": {
        "items": [1, 2]
    }
}

Field name
Type
Requirements
Limitations
items
Array of integers
Required
Number of items is limited only by PHP logic


Example response:
{}
Empty object returns in case of successful deletion
Get Category
Endpoint: api/v3/category/get
Method: GET
Example request: 
{{baseUrl}}/api/v3/category/get?id=25&slug=scaled-metal-models-2

Field name
Type
Requirements
Limitations
id
integer
Required
Exists in the system
