Get all Categories
Endpoint: api/v3/category/get-list
Method: POST
Example request: 
{
    "data": {
        "page": 1,
        "pageSize": 3,
        "filter": {"searchTerm": "models"},
        "sort": "name:asc"
    }
}

Field name
Type
Requirements
Limitations
Description
page
integer
Optional
bigint
Number of the returned page with items
pageSize
integer
Optional
bigint
Number of items per page
filter
object
Optional
Limited system values
searchTerm performs search by name parameter
sort
string
Optional
id:asc, id:desc, name:asc, name:desc
System sorting options

Example response:
{
    "data": {
        "items": [
            {
                "id": 2,
                "name": "Scaled metal models",
                "slug": "scaled-metal-models",
                "showOnMain": true,
                "sortIndex": 1,
                "itemsCount": 14,
                "image": "https://static.dev.alephexpress.com/api/file/get/8e571555-aa73-4cb2-b588-9cb5285795b2/5ca7826cdc9ac57a0c5528c6b056566b_1705051502.jpg",
                "metaTitle": "Scaled metal models",
                "metaDescription": "We sell scaled metal models of cars in 1/43 scaleüöóüöôüöìüöï"
            },
            {
                "id": 25,
                "name": "Scaled metal models test",
                "slug": "scaled-metal-models-2",
                "showOnMain": false,
                "sortIndex": 25,
                "itemsCount": 0,
                "image": "img.jpg",
                "metaTitle": null,
                "metaDescription": null
            }
        ],
        "totalPages": 1,
        "totalItems": 2
    }
}

